4Geeks Academy offers a 16-week Data Science & Machine Learning course. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and Statistics, enabling students to become professional Data Analysts. Students will learn to create predictive models using Python libraries such as Pandas and Numpy, and explore algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees. The course includes real-life case studies and the use of industry-standard tools. Students will also strategize and develop their own AI projects, from development to deployment and maintenance. The course is taught in English or Spanish, and classes are held three times per week with a maximum class size of 12 people. Upon completion, students receive a recognized certificate. For more information, visit the website at https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop